## 10) Testing (pytest)

- Use `pytest` for unit/integration tests.
- Use `pytest-asyncio` for async code.
- Prefer fixtures for shared setup and `@pytest.mark.parametrize` for table-driven cases.

For general Python style guidance, refer to [PEP 8](https://peps.python.org/pep-0008/).
